Script info: Deletes a connection

Input:
  target:
    description: Target service
    default: Digital.ai Release

---
Get accounts: ${target}
As: accounts

---
Prompt:
  description: Select account to delete
  choices: ${accounts}
  type: select one
  display: name
As: account

Delete account:
  target: ${target}
  name: ${account.name}

Print: Deleted ${account.name} in ${target}